{"tid":1073200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真一問 旅行團劏客文化係華人地區特有?","createTime":"2019-03-22T13:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T14:53:21.000Z","uid":159086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51fddfaa17802d94e73440ad46081e999c52e6c3","tid":1073200,"uid":159086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"見好多人跟完旅行團 <br />\n去日本就貴起碼2-3倍既剌身和牛等  仲要沒品質保證<br />\n去大陸就水你買貴N倍既玉石茶壺 過份到可以證書都做假 <br />\n去外國就水你買貴好多維他命 小飾品<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真一問 旅行團領隊導遊劏客文化係華人地區特有?定係全世界都係咁?<br />\n如果我係日本人/歐美人 跟團去香港/大陸都會比人劏得咁勁?定係其實外國已經唔會有旅行團?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟團已經要比固定服務費比領隊導遊 仲要劏爆你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0bb27fe93fb5ef4710f59bb20ee21e3ec79f88b","tid":1073200,"uid":125380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"度度都係咁"},{"pid":"7b39f97a7e6bc763e6b62730ddcd069916f146f3","tid":1073200,"uid":159086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0bb27fe93fb5ef4710f59bb20ee21e3ec79f88b","tid":1073200,"uid":125380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"度度都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"咁黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b466eb059afaf836fb517ad4511423d783fa34ab","tid":1073200,"uid":125380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b39f97a7e6bc763e6b62730ddcd069916f146f3","tid":1073200,"uid":159086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0bb27fe93fb5ef4710f59bb20ee21e3ec79f88b","tid":1073200,"uid":125380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"度度都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"咁黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"所以唔好跟團"},{"pid":"476f12ca3b196584732bb2f47ec2505257ac1274","tid":1073